center_part.Anchored = true
center_part.CanCollide = true
center_part.Parent = script

local offset = CFrame.new(20,20,0)
center_part.CFrame = offset

local target_part = center_part:Clone()
target_part.Parent = script

local hyp_part = center_part:Clone()
hyp_part.Transparency = 0.5
hyp_part.Color = Color3.new(1,0,0)
hyp_part.Parent = script

local adj_part = center_part:Clone()
adj_part.Transparency = 0.5
adj_part.Color = Color3.new(0,1,0)
adj_part.Parent = script

local opp_part = center_part:Clone()
opp_part.Transparency = 0.5
opp_part.Color = Color3.new(0,0,1)
opp_part.Parent = script

local at1 = Instance.new("Attachment")
at1.Position = Vector3.new(0,-0.5,0)
at1.Parent = target_part
local at2 = Instance.new("Attachment")
at1.Position = Vector3.new(0,0.5,0)
at2.Parent = target_part

local trail = Instance.new("Trail")
trail.Attachment0 = at1
trail.Attachment1 = at2
trail.FaceCamera = true
trail.Transparency = NumberSequence.new(0,1)
trail.Lifetime = 1
trail.MinLength = 0
trail.WidthScale = NumberSequence.new(1,1)
trail.Parent = target_part

local angle_change = nil
local hyp_mult = 1
function update()
	local speed = 5
	local dist = 10
	
	local t = os.clock()*speed
	
	target_part.CFrame = offset*CFrame.new(0,math.cos(t)*dist,math.sin(t)*dist)
	
	local pos_sub = (center_part.Position-target_part.Position)*Vector3.new(0,1,1)
	local hyp = pos_sub.Magnitude
	if 0 > pos_sub.Y and hyp_mult == 1 then
		hyp_mult = -1
		
		local s = Instance.new("Sound")
		s.SoundId = 'rbxassetid://2687161647'
		s.Volume = 0.5
		s.PlayOnRemove = true
		s.Parent = target_part
		s:Destroy()
	elseif pos_sub.Y > 0 and hyp_mult == -1 then
		hyp_mult = 1

		local s = Instance.new("Sound")
		s.SoundId = 'rbxassetid://9111926008'
		s.Volume = 0.5
		s.PlayOnRemove = true
		s.Parent = target_part
		s:Destroy()
	end
	hyp = hyp*hyp_mult
	
	local adj = pos_sub.Z
	-- cosA = adj/hyp, A = arccos(adj/hyp)
	local angle = math.acos(adj/hyp)
	angle_change = angle
	-- sinA = opp/hyp, opp = hyp*sin(angle)
	local opp = hyp*math.sin(angle)
	
	hyp_part.Size = Vector3.new(1,1,math.abs(hyp))
	hyp_part.CFrame = offset*CFrame.new(0,-pos_sub.Y/2,-pos_sub.Z/2)*CFrame.Angles(angle*-1,0,0)
	
	adj_part.Size = Vector3.new(1,1,math.abs(adj))
	adj_part.CFrame = offset*CFrame.new(0,0,-pos_sub.Z/2)*CFrame.Angles(0,0,0)
	
	opp_part.Size = Vector3.new(1,math.abs(opp),1)
	opp_part.CFrame = offset*CFrame.new(0,-pos_sub.Y/2,-pos_sub.Z)*CFrame.Angles(0,0,0)
end

while true do
	task.wait()
	update()
end

SELECT d.externalreference AS "ID ",
	   d.tradecurrency AS " ",
	   d.a_productsubtype AS "",
	   d.tradestatus AS "",
	   d.tradeaction AS "",
	   d.version AS " ",
	   TO_DATE(d.a_actual_date, 'YYYY-MM-DD') AS "    ",
       TO_CHAR(TO_TIMESTAMP(d.tradedatetime, 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'), 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS') AS "  ",
       TO_DATE(d.a_fo_adjustedmatdt, 'YYYY-MM-DD') AS "  ",
	   c.longname AS " ",
	   c.country AS ""
FROM "deals.csv" AS d
INNER JOIN (SELECT externalreference,
        		   MAX(version) AS last_version
    		FROM "deals.csv"
    		WHERE tradeaction IN ( 'VERIFY', 'EXECUTE_STP', 'PROCESS', 'MANUAL_EXECUTE', 'TERMINATE', 'TERMINATE_STP', 'FO_TERMINATE') AND tradestatus IN ('VERIFIED', 'TERMINATED')
    		GROUP BY externalreference) last_versions ON d.externalreference = last_versions.externalreference AND d.version = last_versions.last_version
LEFT JOIN "clients.csv" AS c ON d.counterparty_fk = c.id;

template:
  - sensor:
    - name: "Solax_cloud Yield Today"
      state: "{{ state_attr('sensor.solax_cloud', 'yieldtoday') }}"
      unit_of_measurement: "kWh"
      unique_id: XYZ1
      icon: mdi:flash
      device_class: energy
      state_class: total_increasing


    - name: "Solax_cloud Yield Total"
      state: "{{ state_attr('sensor.solax_cloud', 'yieldtotal') }}"
      unit_of_measurement: "kWh"
      unique_id: XYZ2
      icon: mdi:flash
      device_class: energy
      state_class: total_increasing

    - name: "Solax_cloud Inverter Power Total"
      unit_of_measurement: "W"
      state: "{{ state_attr('sensor.solax_cloud', 'acpower') }}"
      unique_id: XYZ3
      icon: mdi:flash
      device_class: energy
      state_class: measurement

    - name: "Solax_cloud Upload Time"
      state: >
        {% set time = state_attr('sensor.solax_cloud', 'uploadTime') %}
        {{ as_timestamp(time) | timestamp_custom('%I:%M %p') }}
      unique_id: XYZ4
      icon: mdi:clock

    - name: "Solax_cloud Battery Status"
      state: "{{ state_attr('sensor.solax_cloud', 'batStatus') }}"
      unique_id: XYZ
      icon: mdi:battery

    - name: "Solax_cloud Solar Panel"
      state: "{{ state_attr('sensor.solax_cloud', 'powerdc1') + state_attr('sensor.solax_cloud', 'powerdc2') }}"
      unit_of_measurement: "W"
      device_class: energy
      state_class: measurement
      unique_id: XYZ5
      icon: mdi:solar-power-variant

    - name: "Solax_cloud Battery Use"
      state: "{{ state_attr('sensor.solax_cloud', 'batPower') }}"
      unit_of_measurement: "W"
      device_class: energy
      state_class: measurement
      unique_id: XYZ6
      icon: mdi:battery

    - name: "Solax_cloud Battery Use In"
      state: >
        {% set attr = state_attr('sensor.solax_cloud', 'batPower') %}
        {{ attr if is_number(attr) and (attr|float > 0) else 0 }}
      unit_of_measurement: "W"
      unique_id: XYZ7
      icon: mdi:battery

    - name: "Solax_cloud Battery Use Out"
      state: >
        {% set attr = state_attr('sensor.solax_cloud', 'batPower') %}
        {{ (0 - attr) if is_number(attr) and (attr|float < 0) else 0 }}
      unit_of_measurement: "W"
      unique_id: XYZ8
      icon: mdi:battery

    - name: "Solax_cloud Battery"
      state: "{{ state_attr('sensor.solax_cloud', 'soc') }}"
      unit_of_measurement: "%"
      device_class: battery
      state_class: measurement
      unique_id: XYZ9
      icon: mdi:battery

    - name: "Solax_cloud Grid Power"
      state: >
        {% set attr = state_attr('sensor.solax_cloud', 'feedinpower') %}
        {{ (0 - attr) if is_number(attr) else 0 }}
      unit_of_measurement: "W"
      device_class: energy
      state_class: measurement
      unique_id: XYZ10
      icon: mdi:transmission-tower

    - name: "Solax_cloud Grid Power in"
      state: >
        {% set attr = state_attr('sensor.solax_cloud', 'feedinpower') %}
        {{ (0 - attr) if is_number(attr) and (attr|float < 0) else 0 }}
      unit_of_measurement: "W"
      unique_id: XYZ11
      icon: mdi:transmission-tower

    - name: "Solax_cloud Grid Power out"
      state: >
        {% set attr = state_attr('sensor.solax_cloud', 'feedinpower') %}
        {{ attr if is_number(attr) and (attr|float > 0) else 0 }}
      unit_of_measurement: "W"
      unique_id: XYZ12
      icon: mdi:transmission-tower

    - name: "Solax_cloud Energy To Grid"
      state: "{{ state_attr('sensor.solax_cloud', 'feedinenergy') }}"
      unit_of_measurement: "kWh"
      unique_id: XYZ13
      icon: mdi:transmission-tower
      device_class: energy
      state_class: total_increasing

    - name: "Solax_cloud Energy From Grid"
      state: "{{ state_attr('sensor.solax_cloud', 'consumeenergy') }}"
      unit_of_measurement: "kWh"
      unique_id: XYZ14
      icon: mdi:transmission-tower
      device_class: energy
      state_class: total_increasing

    - name: "Solax_cloud Status"
      unique_id: XYZ15
      icon: mdi:solar-power-variant
      state: >
          {% set attr = state_attr('sensor.solax_cloud', 'inverterStatus') %}
          {% if attr == '100' %}Wait
          {% elif attr == '101' %}Check
          {% elif attr == '102' %}Normal
          {% elif attr == '103' %}Fault
          {% elif attr == '104' %}Permanent Fault
          {% elif attr == '105' %}Update
          {% elif attr == '106' %}EPS Check
          {% elif attr == '107' %}EPS
          {% elif attr == '108' %}Self-test
          {% elif attr == '109' %}Idle
          {% elif attr == '110' %}Standby
          {% elif attr == '111' %}Pv Wake Up Bat
          {% elif attr == '112' %}Gen Check
          {% elif attr == '113' %}Gen Run
          {% else %}unknown{% endif %}
